OL,7,     Gtrip to an old mill proves to be
OL,8,     Ginexplicably popular. More so
OL,9,     Gthan Dean's supposedly legendary
OL,10,     Gbreakfast, anyway...
OL,11,G1300FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GPeace. Tranquillity. Relaxation.
OL,13,     GUnfortunately, it's payment day,
OL,14,     Gso there's none of that here.
